==English==
[[Category:Mammals]]
===Noun===
'''panda''' ([[pandas]], [[pandae]])

# Black and white [[bear]]-like [[animal]], ''Ailuropoda melanoleuca'' from the [[mountain]]s of [[China]]. Eats shoots and leaves.
# A small [[raccoon]]-like animal, ''Ailurus fulgens'' of northeast [[Asia]] with reddish fur and a long [[ringed]] [[tail]]

====Synonyms====
*[[giant panda]] (1)
*[[Mottled Bear]]<!-- not sure about capitalisation --> (?)
*[[panda bear]] (1)
*[[lesser panda]] (2)
*[[red panda]] (2)


